---
description: Use the Axin personal IP illustration workflow in this repository
globs:
  - "**/*.md"
alwaysApply: false
---

When working on this repository, treat `axin-personal-ip-illustrations/SKILL.md` as the source of truth.

Generate or document illustrations as 16:9 Chinese article images with pure white background, minimalist hand-drawn black line art, sparse red/orange/blue handwritten notes, and a character performing the core action.

Use 阿鑫 / Axin as the default and only recurring character: a hand-drawn human with black hair, round glasses, and a hoodie.

For repository edits, run `scripts/validate-repo.ps1` before finalizing.
